         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">30/12/86 ¶ Allow me to mention, dear Mr Jackson, that you might be able at a very moderate expenditure, to obtain the experienced aid of Herr J. A. Knapp of Vienne. for your great opus. ¶ for your gre...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">86.05.30a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">
               <seg style="">To B. Daydon Jackson</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">
               <seg style="">Linnean Society of London, Archives, MS-338a-15.</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">30/12/86</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Allow me to mention, dear Mr Jackson, that you might be able at a very moderate expenditure, to obtain the experienced aid of Herr J. A. Knapp of Vienne. for your great opus.</seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                     <p rend="Footnote"
                        style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg style="">
                           <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>for your great opus </seg>
                        <seg style="font-style: italic; ">interlined between sentences.</seg>
                        <seg style=""> Jackson had been working on the compilation of what became </seg>
                        <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Index Kewensis </seg>
                        <seg style="">(Jackson (1895)) since 1881, see Jackson (1924).</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> This Gentleman, as you may be aware, has been engaged for years in botanical Bibliography at the Vienne Apotheker-Verein. His engagement there, which was an inexpensive one, has closed since he returned from a botanical Journey to Persia, the tour — I believe — being made on his own expense.</seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                     <p rend="Footnote"
                        style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg style="">
                           <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>But see his entry in </seg>
                        <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Österreichisches Biographisches Lexikon </seg>(<ref target="http://www.biographien.ac.at/oebl/oebl_K/Knapp_Josef-Armin_1843_1899.xml"
                             rend="Internet%20link"
                             style="color: #0563c1; ">
                           <seg rend="Internet%20link" style="color: #0563c1; ">http://www.biographien.ac.at/oebl/oebl_K/Knapp_Josef-Armin_1843_1899.xml</seg>
                        </ref>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="2"/>(accessed 14 October 2020)),<seg style=""> which reports that his trip was financed by Jacob Pollak, an Austrian physician and explorer who had worked in Persia in the 1850s-1860s. Some of his collections from this trip are described by specialists in Wettstein (1889).</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> Mr Knapp could be communicated with through Prof. Dr. Kerner, the Director of the botanic Garden of Vienna.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>What a </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">boon</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> your name-lists will be for all times! I shall not likely live to benefit from them.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>With best felicitation at the anniversary of of</seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                     <p rend="Footnote"
                        style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg style="">
                           <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg style="font-style: italic; ">word repeated</seg>
                        <seg style="">: our?</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> Christian era</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg style="">Yours,<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</seg>
            </p>
         </div>
